{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"CANGLONG4","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["Together with Souryuu\n\n<size=45>Chapter 4: Unnecessary Things...?<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"side":2,"bgm":"story-1","say":"Port - Sakura Dorms","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"dir":1,"bgmDelay":2,"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]}},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"On my day off, I once again found myself headed for Souryuu's room, looking to relax and recover.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Did you need to see my sister?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307040},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":1,"say":"Commander, though you're free to spend your day off however you please, I'd recommend you do something more worthwhile.","paintingFadeOut":{"time":0.5,"side":0},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","actor":307030},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"withoutActorName":true,"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"As she spoke, she was still working on documents that she had brought back from the office yesterday. Truly a model secretary.","actor":307030},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"*sigh*...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307040},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I wonder when I'll be able to help the Commander like this...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307040},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"If that's what you really want, you'd better start studying harder from now on.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"\"I agree.\""}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"That's not what I meant... When you're working hard like this, you look really beautiful. Don't you think so too, Commander?","actor":307040},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"*sigh*... What are you talking about? There's nothing beautiful about this.?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Err, I dunno, I'm not so great with words... but Akagi said something about \"a woman's allure?\"","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307040},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Listen, Hiryuu. This is simply what is expected of every member of the fleet. My relationship with the Commander has nothing to do with this.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"This has nothing to do with a \"woman's allure\" or that \"girlishness\" thing that you're always talking about, understood?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"withoutActorName":true,"side":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Wow... Souryuu was being colder than usual.","actor":307030},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Well, isn't there something that you'd want to do to improve your girlishness?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307040},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"What are you... why in the world would I want to do something like that?","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ah, um, hear me out! I really think you're beautiful, Souryuu, and that includes when you're being cold too. However, I sometimes want to see more aspects of your personality!","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307040},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"*sigh*...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But... Hmm. There just might be a way to get me to change.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030},{"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"\"I'd like to know, too.\""}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"action":[{"number":2,"x":0,"type":"shake","delay":0,"dur":0.15,"y":45}],"nameColor":"#a9f548","dir":1,"say":"Eh? Really?!","actor":307040},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I wonder, what should I do...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_room","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Was it just my imagination, or did Souryuu just steal a sideways glance at me?","blackBg":true,"dir":1}]}